the cards as the elevator is moved up and down cards are randomly inserted into one of the 1 shelves in the elevator the shuffler randomly selects a shelf of cards to deliver into the shoe because of the nonlinear process every discard reinserted following a hand has a chance of appearing in the next round  although shuffle master says the king differs from their competitors continuous shufflers because the others use a linear design most csms so the same thing they put the discards back into play and does away with the dealers having to stop to physically shuffle the cards at the end of a shoe nthe house edge  the continuous shufflers have no benefits for the player and has been dubbed the uncomfortable shoes it eli aminates card counting for the skilled player and will also have a entirely true michael shackleford the wizard of odds did a mathematical analysis of the continuous shuffling machines and found that there was a very slight reduction in the house edge nin a four deck game the edge is 00 percent and in an eight deck game is tis001 percent before you get excited about a slight reduction in the house edge you have to realize that when the casino uses a csm the speed
